# agate

> A simple server for the Gemini network protocol
> More information: https://github.com/mbrubeck/agate

- Run and generate a private key and certificate:

`agate --content {string value: path/to/content/} --addr {string value: [::]:1965} --addr {string value: 0.0.0.0:1965} --hostname {string value: example.com} --lang {string value: en-US}`

- Run server:

`agate {file value}`

- Display help:

`agate -h`
